column1: I understand the information presented on FMCG product labels and am satisfied with the clarity of these claims.
column2: How clear and visible do you find environmental claims on FMCG product packaging?
column3: How much does the presence of environmental claims on FMCG products influence your purchasing decisions?
column4: Would you be willing to pay more for an FMCG product with verified and transparent environmental claims, even if the price is higher than misleading products?
